jack and jill is a 2011 american comedy film directed by dennis dugan , written by steve koren and adam sandler , and starring sandler , katie holmes , and al pacino . the film was released on november 11 , 2011 by columbia pictures . the film was widely panned by critics and has since been considered to be one of the worst films ever made . jack and jill " won " all 10 golden raspberry awards for 2011 , breaking battlefield earth 's record for the most razzie wins for a single film .